### 7.11 API response for frontend permission UI

Frontend should not guess labels, sections, modules, or permission names.

Recommended endpoints:

```php
Route::middleware(['auth:sanctum'])->group(function () {
    Route::get('/me/permissions', CurrentUserPermissionsController::class);
    Route::get('/permission-groups', PermissionGroupsController::class);
});
```

Use cases:

- `/me/permissions`: current user granted permissions and boolean map.
- `/permission-groups`: full permission catalog for role forms, checkbox lists, and dashboard screens.

Recommended response shape:

```json
{
